{"tid":1559251,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"藍黃商店分辦大法  和理非同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-10T17:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T01:48:37.000Z","uid":91659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69680493b96e9a1d1db7cf5a9b6b95f5e2728845","tid":1559251,"uid":91659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"好多巴絲都分唔到邊間店舖係咩立場，萬一入左間藍店食野真係背脊骨落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如我地從自己嘅社區做起，用一個簡單嘅符號貼喺已 fact check 立場嘅舖頭度，咁搵野食買野就容易得多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n具體操作：<br />\n<br />\n1. 決定一個冇冒犯性嘅標記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（例如黃色同藍色 memo 紙，淨色貼紙.etc）<br />\n<br />\n2. 決定用作辨認嘅位置 （例如每間鋪頭嘅門口右下角）<br />\n<br />\n3. Fact check 確認店舖是否推薦光顧<br />\n<br />\n4. 輕輕將標記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貼上，大功告成。<br />\n<br />\n以後每去一間店鋪前，都順手望一下門口右下角有冇標記：藍貼紙就唔好入，黃貼紙就買買買，唔洗下下上網 check <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項<br />\n<br />\n1. 標記不宜過大，以免被太多人發現清除<br />\n<br />\n2. 不宜用藍黃貼紙等意識明顯嘅標記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可用其他顏色圖案，大家 get 到就得<br />\n<br />\n3. 確認左先好貼，免殺錯無辜<br />\n<br />\n4. 要張貼在不會被貨物遮住嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要大家養成順手望一眼嘅小習慣，就可以為香港本地出一分力，而且完全合法零風險！零風險！零風險！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nforward 去各區 tg 實踐下～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e73b04c03d88269d29630249a97aca578b634c7","tid":1559251,"uid":67043,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/z4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2Fz4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=2a1d7a47\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/z4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8</a><br />\n<br />\n新時代消費地圖，個網係google地圖嚟，login 後，之後可以係返google map度睇返<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UexC8FQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUexC8FQ.jpg&h=c706bb98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83b1fed6e8a7c17b6f53ebdd5403a87ff3b79868","tid":1559251,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e73b04c03d88269d29630249a97aca578b634c7","tid":1559251,"uid":67043,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/z4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2Fz4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=2a1d7a47\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/z4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8</a><br />\n<br />\n新時代消費地圖，個網係google地圖嚟，login 後，之後可以係返google map度睇返<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UexC8FQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUexC8FQ.jpg&h=c706bb98&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:57:34.000Z","msg":"樓主推呢個仲實際，有齊背景"},{"pid":"368d86d1a74e233aefe0c46929c4399f70ec9f9a","tid":1559251,"uid":182795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e73b04c03d88269d29630249a97aca578b634c7","tid":1559251,"uid":67043,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/z4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2Fz4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRegNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=2a1d7a47\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/z4k8CE7n92Q3u6pW8</a><br />\n<br />\n新時代消費地圖，個網係google地圖嚟，login 後，之後可以係返google map度睇返<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UexC8FQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUexC8FQ.jpg&h=c706bb98&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"push<br />\ndl左幾個google map legend<br />\n消費之前睇睇"},{"pid":"5b9b8c6b1d0044e3ee1d58a502e3c12e4de6ce0a","tid":1559251,"uid":182795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor